                    img.guestbook-slider__photo(src="img/section_guestbook/photo-1.jpg")
                    div.guestbook-slider__text.guestbook-slider__text_short I never meant to cause you any sorrow. I never meant to cause you any pain. I only wanted to one time see you laughing. I only wanted to see you laughing in the purple rain.
                    div.guestbook-slider__author Emma Stone
                div.guestbook-slider__item.guestbook-slider__item_single
                    img.guestbook-slider__photo(src="img/section_guestbook/photo-2.jpg")
                    div.guestbook-slider__text.guestbook-slider__text_short People always told me be careful of what you do And dont go around breaking young girls' hearts And mother always told me be careful of who you love And be careful of what you do cause the lie becomes the truth.
