                div.guestbook-slider__item.guestbook-slider__item_single
                    img.guestbook-slider__photo(src="img/section_guestbook/photo-3.jpg")
                    div.guestbook-slider__text.guestbook-slider__text_short Oh, a storm is threat'ning My very life today If I don't get some shelter Oh yeah, I'm gonna fade away.
